        title: { tr: "KKTC İşletmeleri İçin SMS ve WhatsApp Business Pazarlama", en: "SMS & WhatsApp Business Marketing for Businesses in North Cyprus" },
        excerpt: { tr: "KKTC'de SMS pazarlama ve WhatsApp Business API ile müşterilerinize anında ulaşın. BC Creative Agency ile mobil pazarlama stratejinizi güçlendirin. Girne'den tüm KKTC'ye hizmet.", en: "Reach your customers instantly in North Cyprus with SMS marketing and WhatsApp Business API. Strengthen your mobile marketing strategy with BC Creative Agency. Serving all of North Cyprus from Kyrenia." },
        category: "Dijital Pazarlama",
